      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "TO: DIRECTOR FBI",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "DATE: 11-8-57",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "FROM: SAC KANSAS CITY (66-2995)",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "INFORMATION CONCERNING",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "On November 5, 1957, SA (A) [REDACTED] received",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "information from Mr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Kansas City, Missouri that an uncle, [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "or [REDACTED], employed by an aircraft concern and",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "residing at Fort Worth, Texas, about two years ago saw an",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "unidentified subject in the sky near his home. He obtained",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "his movie camera and took pictures of the object. About",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "eighteen months ago the uncle visited in Kansas City and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "the movies of the flying disc were shown. According to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "[REDACTED] the pictures were very good and consisted of about",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "fifteen feet of film.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] stated that he and his uncle have felt \"foolish\"",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "when discussing the matter and never bothered to report it.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "He said however in view of the late international developments",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "he felt that the Government should have this information.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "In view of the fact that the Bureau may be interested",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "in this film, it is requested that the Dallas Office at",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Fort Worth, Texas locate and interview [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "or [REDACTED] and obtain the film for transmittal",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "to the Bureau.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "It is suggested that the Bureau, after reviewing the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "film, advise the Office of Special Investigations, USAF,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "of any pertinent information deemed appropriate.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
